altername_name: Enomoto Kanako no Boke Shindan Game
name: Kanako Enomoto: Junk Brain Diagnosis
overview: Kanako Enomoto Junk Brain Diagnosis is a collection of wacky mini games that allows one player mode or group mode (with up to 8 human players using the multitap controller). The goal of the game is to pass the different diagnosis to determinate if you're sane or not...
